        "output_symbol": "THINK TWICE BEFORE DOING MODIFIER KEYDOWN IN A IN ANY MACRO!\nSome applications listen for that (think firefox!)\n\nONLY CTRL L WILL TOGGLE KEYBINDS!\nI use it a lot, and I really don't want to send .key_up(Ctrl_L).key_up(Ctrl_R)\neverytime I want to do anything\n\n\n<Alt-Alt> = \\\n\n<Shift-Shift> = generate fighting one eyed kirby and places you inside it\n\n<C-h> = <Esc> (disables caps lock if its on)\n<C-,> = <Home> (shift compatible to select a line)\n<C-.> = <End>  (^)\n\n<C-S-BS> = Delete whole line\n",
